body_raw:
Let $\mu$, $
u$ be two Radon Measure on $\mathbb{R}^n$. How can I prove that $D_{\mu}{
u}=\lim_{r 	o 0}  rac{
u(B(x,r)}{\mu(B(x,r))}$ is in $L^1_{loc}(\mathbb{R}^n,\mu)$?

